            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-tech-teal mr-3 mt-1">✓</span>
              <span><strong>Collateral Documentation:</strong> If you're pledging assets (equipment, property, inventory) as collateral, you'll need appraisals and titles.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-tech-teal mr-3 mt-1">✓</span>
              <span><strong>Debt Schedule:</strong> A list of all current business debts, monthly payments, and balances owed.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-tech-teal mr-3 mt-1">✓</span>
              <span><strong>SBA Form 1919:</strong> Borrower Information Form (your lender will provide this).</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-tech-teal mr-3 mt-1">✓</span>
              <span><strong>SBA Form 413:</strong> Personal Financial Statement (standard form for all owners with 20%+ ownership).</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
